videos.description: Evina Westbrook makes draining 3-pointers look easy as she sinks a pair on consecutive possessions in the second half.

videos.description: Christyn Williams goes backdoor to pick up Dorka Juhasz's laser in the fourth quarter of UConn's dominant win over Marquette.
